def custom_fib(signature, indexes, n):
    if n < len(signature):
        return signature[n]
    
    seq = signature[:]
    
    for i in range(len(signature), n + 1):
        next_value = sum(seq[j] for j in indexes)
        seq.append(next_value)
        seq.pop(0)  # Maintain the length of the signature
    
    return seq[-1]
```
